Package: cr3
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, cr3-settings
Description: e-book reader
 CoolReader3 is an e-book reader.
 .
 Main features:
  * supports several open e-book formats: fb2, html, epub, rtf,
    tcr (psion text), plain text
  * reads directly from zip archives
  * automatically determines encodings
  * automatically generates a table of contents
  * keeps the last open book and the last read positions for all open books
    between runs
  * automatic hyphenation (patterns for several languages are included)
 .
  Homepage: http://www.coolreader.org/

